title: Proposal to Boost the PMON-BUSD Farm
body:
# PancakeSwap Welcomes Back Polychain Monsters to Syrup Pool!

CAKE holders, today we are very happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from Polychain Monsters, beautifully animated cross-chain NFTs which can be unpacked from digital booster packs with $PMON.


# What is Boost?
Boost is basically an increase in farm multiplier over a set period of time, which is offered in exchange for additional tokens from the boosted project, which are then put into a new Syrup Pool!

So basically, PMON-BUSD will go from a 0.5x multiple to a 1x multiple, which will last for 30 DAYS, which will only cause temporary dilution among the other farms, and at the same time, there will be a new PMON Syrup Pool with $200K of tokens, to be earned by staking CAKE.



# The Syrup Pool:
Stake CAKE tokens to earn PMON tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 46,600 PMON
- **Distribution duration:** 60 days
- **Start block:** 9317900 (approx. 9am UTC on July 20th)
- **Finish block:** 11045900 (approx. 9am UTC on September 18th)
- **Token rewards per block:** 0.02696 PMON


## Max Stake per wallet: 
100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards. 

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some juicy pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.

# What is Polychain Monsters?

Polychain Monsters are beautifully animated cross-chain NFTs with varying scarcity, waiting for you to be discovered in digital booster packs. These NFTs will play an integral part in upcoming off- and on-chain games. In addition, Polychain Monsters offers DeFi features such as $PMON & NFT staking.



### To learn more about Polychain Monsters, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website:** [https://polychainmonsters.com/](https://polychainmonsters.com/)
- **Twitter:** [https://twitter.com/polychainmon](https://twitter.com/polychainmon)
- **Telegram:** [https://t.me/polychainmonsters](https://t.me/polychainmonsters)
- **Medium:** [https://medium.com/polychainmonsters](https://medium.com/polychainmonsters)


# How do you stake CAKE to earn PMON rewards?
If you own CAKE tokens, congratulations! You’re the master of your … pancakes.
Time to step up your taste buds by learning how to stake CAKE with Syrup Pool.
- Visit this webpage: [**https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup** ](https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup )
- Click “Approve CAKE” on the PMON Syrup Pool 
- Click on the stake button.
- Confirm the transaction.

# BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official PMON token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:
[**https://bscscan.com/address/0x1796ae0b0fa4862485106a0de9b654eFE301D0b2**](https://bscscan.com/address/0x1796ae0b0fa4862485106a0de9b654eFE301D0b2)

Any other PMON token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss for users. Do not buy tokens from any other token address. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive airdrops from another address for PMON tokens, they will be rotten tokens (but not the cool kind!), and we advise you to ignore them.
